Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.31,0:00:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您的惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.29,0:00:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.27,0:00:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一點都不喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.11,0:00:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只拿了一個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.60,0:00:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.75,0:00:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來找小都的  不過看來不在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.40,0:00:40.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都？宮崎同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.53,0:00:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便說一下我還會再來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:23.04,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}第10話\N宮崎都的憂鬱和初次大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.59,0:02:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.07,0:02:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是老酒鋪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.87,0:02:40.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生意還不錯嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:42.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別傻了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.65,0:02:46.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  不是比酒鋪的時候更賺嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.59,0:02:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知不知道要回交公司多少錢啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要支出人事費用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.87,0:02:53.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒賺多少
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.06,0:03:00.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比以前更拼命  卻沒怎麼賺頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:02.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:08.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎侍  你既然回來了就別在家無所事事  快去店裡幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.74,0:03:14.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來老媽  我的飯呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.78,0:03:16.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都快餓死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.83,0:03:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:23.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:27.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…喂  這不是店裡的商品嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.58,0:03:30.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且馬上就要過保質期了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.61,0:03:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說了嘛  貨款有一半都是爸爸媽媽在出嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不做咖喱嗎？兒子難得回來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.91,0:03:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴給我吃！然後去幹活！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸老媽成天都吃這個！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.25,0:03:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  虎侍  你也要幫忙分擔家計
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.36,0:03:51.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我知道了  吃就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來還想吃老媽做的咖喱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.98,0:03:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題  這裡有的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了  全是商品而且還快過保質期了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.62,0:04:06.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充斥在童年回憶那懷念的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太幼稚了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.13,0:04:10.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該變得像個大人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.34,0:04:16.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎侍  你晚上來店裡幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:19.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.87,0:04:22.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:31.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真辛苦啊  老爸老媽比以前更勞累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不能讓學校解雇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能靠家裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼沒有香蕉牛奶了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我平常都有買嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:50.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  那商品現在已經停止生產了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:52.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？沒法再進貨了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:54.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  都不考慮到客人的需求  真沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  沒想法了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.73,0:05:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算對我們說這樣事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:10.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人社會裡看到也要當作沒看到的沒道理的事情太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.40,0:05:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發脾氣也解決不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:19.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒道理…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.39,0:05:21.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來幫忙真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.39,0:05:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從店鋪改成這樣後你就沒回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫石田！請多多指教！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:35.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  真有精神啊  多大了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:38.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十八了  大學一年級
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:40.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為開始自己住所以要開始賺錢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎是嗎  要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近很不太平呢  特別是深夜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:50.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斜對面那家  去年還被搶過了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.64,0:05:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我們有兩個人  不過別太放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.81,0:05:56.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我經常偷懶的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.23,0:06:02.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧！我有在練劍道的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我一把竹劍  來個強盜什麼一下就把他搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.73,0:06:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可真放心啊  那我去拿一把過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.67,0:06:16.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  客人來了  把竹劍收好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.27,0:06:28.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把錢拿出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要報警…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.47,0:06:44.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:48.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石田君  電話是多少來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.81,0:06:51.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是多少呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:07:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起來  我那時開始就逃避  放棄  裝看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:03.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不記得有戰鬥過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生最大的敵人就是沒道理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.95,0:07:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與對錯無關  只是必須接受的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.09,0:07:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人的社會  是沒有任何答案的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:20.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與自己的人生！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,420元
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.01,0:07:41.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.16,0:07:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我到時候再回來咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.14,0:07:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是老爸給你的零用錢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  不用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.15,0:07:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了  拿去吧  你不是也幫過忙了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.36,0:08:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這倒也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:06.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好花吧  別去買什麼無聊的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我是小孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:19.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五萬…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:25.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是當了一晚的班
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.05,0:08:27.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太讓我窩心了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是  小田島禮美？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:36.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我同年還一本正經的叫我小都…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢…她好像在偷東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:42.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是禮美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.95,0:08:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的學校就在這附近的車站旁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我們念同所中學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  上了高中還不放過我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:56.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然歸還了商品但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:08:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是通知她家裡人比較好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:08:59.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長！不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:02.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她家人很難纏的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.51,0:09:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我不在這裡做的話就完事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個死丫頭片子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但川添同學也只做到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會很困擾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你來前台不就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.94,0:09:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:22.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也是呢  不能總麻煩你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:26.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:28.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的薪水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:31.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間謝謝你  幫了我很大的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.52,0:09:35.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是  謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:39.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.63,0:09:42.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在你已經能招呼客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:46.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始我以為你要做到這點還太早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然年輕就是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能進一步成長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.93,0:09:57.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該說年輕嗎？還很小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:03.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天沒有側座啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  宮崎同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.63,0:10:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.03,0:10:10.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才說的那個人…沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.93,0:10:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田島禮美？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係沒關係  小珠你不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.16,0:10:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  小珠你是為什麼想來打工的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.75,0:10:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.48,0:10:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因為動畫的初回特典版DVDBOX就要發行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.55,0:10:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…能面不改色的說出這種事情也是小珠風格吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮崎同學呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了給段郎買禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.18,0:10:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎的生日就快要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.52,0:10:43.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:46.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就是段郎的生日啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  糟了  我都忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.06,0:10:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  小珠  我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.61,0:10:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是榮花同學的生日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.71,0:11:04.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:16.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  祝你生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.47,0:11:18.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄Material Puzzle的DVD吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:40.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下沒幹勁啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公你聽我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田邊家的義男好像沒考上大學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.33,0:11:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經是第二次了吧  真糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:11:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.06,0:11:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:12:00.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮美  要好好做作業哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:17.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.81,0:12:19.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎當主角咯～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.72,0:12:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice Couple…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一名！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:52.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小次郎老師真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.67,0:12:53.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好少見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  已經來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:12:59.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是部長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.79,0:13:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,許久不經歷的大賽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:02.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出氣勢來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.18,0:13:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有氣勢！就不會被解雇！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.17,0:13:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是很無聊的動機…不過我還是很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.12,0:13:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使無法達成夢想  只要有這個心情就滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼「只要有這個心情」  我可是要被開除的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人越來越多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.87,0:13:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共有十五所學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過女生要少得多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.40,0:13:33.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有學校一個女生都找不到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  女子劍道本來人就很少
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:41.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  「獲勝率增加」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.86,0:13:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的珠姬可是第一啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.18,0:13:45.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全國第一啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:47.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不期待團體戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.61,0:13:50.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的比賽就當作珠姬全國制霸的前哨戰吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.21,0:13:52.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們怎麼樣都無所謂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.18,0:13:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  說人人到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:13:58.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:01.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要放到哪裡好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要繞到後面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有桑原前輩  小都都和榮花
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明說了8點半集合…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.91,0:14:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來打個電話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.89,0:14:26.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思——！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.24,0:14:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡過頭了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為昨晚突然有文章在我的腦海裡忽隱忽現
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發覺過來的時候就睡了  醒來的時候就已經過8點了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.80,0:14:41.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是睡過了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.87,0:14:44.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  文章沒記下來不就沒有意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  小都都？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.68,0:14:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你人在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎他迷路了  我正在找他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市民體育館在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:14:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去換衣服先
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:02.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上有個人戰  都拿出氣勢來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.42,0:15:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你們看女生那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:28.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡是最高大的那個和最小塊的選手在對戰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.23,0:15:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.33,0:15:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:36.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面有效
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.57,0:15:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎快點換衣服！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上要輪到段君上場了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.24,0:15:49.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.12,0:15:52.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:54.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.92,0:15:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬歲！萬歲！萬歲！萬歲！…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.08,0:16:18.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早知道  能優勝太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鞘  你能進到二戰也很出色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:27.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…不過和小珠比起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:30.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意  拿來比就不對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.68,0:16:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次  你的對手不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:37.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一回戰就遇見全國級選手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.79,0:16:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次輸了也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.91,0:16:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.97,0:16:42.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真令人激動啊  全國級的水平
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  段君呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.25,0:16:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那啥表情？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:51.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎可是第二名哦！第二名！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:54.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯！很厲害吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:56.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,0:16:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手不是請假就是比你還外行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不然就是因為肚子疼而棄權…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.68,0:17:05.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣得來的第二名…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.43,0:17:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝利就是勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.57,0:17:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:11.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.89,0:17:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午是團體戰  你和紀梨乃接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.48,0:17:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃？紀梨乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.21,0:17:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊被中學時代的朋友逮住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她交際很廣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.40,0:17:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在重要的作戰會議兼重要的午餐會上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.66,0:17:30.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只有指望她家的可樂餅了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.96,0:17:33.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說  被襲擊了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:34.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找她回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.38,0:17:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中學時候的朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:42.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不想見以前認識的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:45.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.44,0:17:46.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色溢出來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.41,0:17:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女子個人優勝是紀梨乃你們學校的一年級吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.31,0:17:54.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿  很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:56.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明那麼嬌小
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.79,0:17:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.79,0:17:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吃午飯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  你們等等做前輩的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的一年級可就差遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.41,0:18:07.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也好好學學人家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:10.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小尾巴翹太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.74,0:18:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.21,0:18:14.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是室江高的新生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為是東呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  東？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天東沒有來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:24.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們部裡面沒有姓東的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.24,0:18:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了  東她的確念室江高吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.97,0:18:32.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再練劍道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.99,0:18:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我們中學最強的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:37.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上高中後放棄了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.43,0:18:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:41.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:44.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎～啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.63,0:18:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:48.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:52.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都的也～啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.54,0:18:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:14.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是  小田島禮美？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:15.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的幻覺吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼那傢伙在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.33,0:19:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說  那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.85,0:19:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算上了高中依然要糾纏我？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.90,0:19:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來她真的開始練劍道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.99,0:19:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍道服好合適你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你變漂亮了  小都
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.94,0:19:42.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午後將進行團體戰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:46.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出戰的各位請到館內來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.63,0:19:49.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！不甘心！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:52.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是再冷靜一點就能贏了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.38,0:19:54.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就能上二回戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.33,0:20:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果團體戰獲勝的只有小珠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.74,0:20:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方也是四個人所以人數少不是理由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.66,0:20:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生普遍都少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:13.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都看起來是不是怪怪的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.91,0:20:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近看起來蠻可疑的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽的時候也無精打采
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.93,0:20:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是碰到了中學時候的朋友啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！她說過不想見到這類人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:30.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣！她遇到了不想碰見知道她過去的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.43,0:20:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.45,0:20:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答對了  給你加十分…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.91,0:20:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…宮崎同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不進道場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:44.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  小珠  我進我進
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.06,0:20:50.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇死我了  她總是毫無聲息的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:54.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慘  最近總是平靜不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.72,0:20:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是籠罩在禮美的陰影下…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.32,0:21:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都  我們一起去學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.78,0:21:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很奇怪  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.85,0:21:08.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.88,0:21:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天大家表現不錯！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.67,0:21:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  下次的IH大賽預選才是來真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.03,0:21:17.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標是獲勝！進軍全國！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.68,0:21:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.23,0:21:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好加油  我就請你們吃超好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.44,0:21:24.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上限五萬元！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.60,0:21:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.46,0:21:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五萬元？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.48,0:21:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎？老師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.38,0:21:30.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是看錯了兩個零？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.53,0:21:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師壞掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.48,0:21:33.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.13,0:21:40.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  小都都狀態也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.58,0:21:44.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得趕快找到第五個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.39,0:21:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小次郎老師  關於這件事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好真有哦  第五人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.96,0:21:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.35,0:22:02.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是誰來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.95,0:22:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.14,0:22:22.82,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:27.84,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}夕闇に  輝き出す  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.14,0:22:34.23,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.26,0:22:55.29,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}窓辺で素足のまま  夜を見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.74,0:23:02.32,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眠れない 月明かり ひとり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.19,0:23:10.19,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目の前を ちらついてく 昼間の私
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:17.53,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}自分だけ 空回りで もどかしいまま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.81,0:23:20.49,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.78,0:23:25.53,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目を閉じて  心の声  聞いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:32.37,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まだ知らない 私に出会いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.53,0:23:35.37,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.62,0:23:40.37,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まばゆく  輝いてる  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.70,0:23:48.05,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.14,0:22:22.82,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:27.84,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}暮色中閃耀著的那小小心願
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.14,0:22:34.23,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄於手中  希望流星能為我實現…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.26,0:22:55.29,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在窗邊光著腳丫  仰望著夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.74,0:23:02.32,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}唯有無法入眠的月光相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.19,0:23:10.19,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眼前浮現出午時的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:17.53,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只是徒勞得令人著急
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.81,0:23:20.49,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.78,0:23:25.53,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}閉上眼睛傾聽心中的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:32.37,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}依然無法得知  它想與我相見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.53,0:23:35.37,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.62,0:23:40.37,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}光輝而耀眼的那小小心願
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.70,0:23:48.05,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄於手中  希望流星能為我實現…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.82,0:23:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.79,0:23:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱是紀梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.58,0:23:53.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日月輪轉快又快
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.18,0:23:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱們竹劍終於也超過十話突入十回戰啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.66,0:23:59.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.34,0:23:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓掌鼓掌
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.06,0:24:00.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過獎過獎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.76,0:24:02.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  現在正在做
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.20,0:24:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宣傳部長狀態正佳！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.66,0:24:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.64,0:24:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在搜尋仍未出現的第五人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.11,0:24:09.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實行捕獲成為同伴的充滿陰謀的任務中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.32,0:24:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和小鞘會全力以赴的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.16,0:24:11.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話的標題是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.20,0:24:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「動畫與夢境」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.88,0:24:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒什麼事還是沒看下一話的話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.25,0:24:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉出去再教育
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.16,0:24:18.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以節目來講就是場外！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.51,0:24:19.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合起來就是！一本！
